metadata.description:
Minted on Fibonacci New Year's Day (1/1/22), this was Scott's first token minted on Manifold. 

The image, which might well be just a placeholder, is an homage to Haiku #3 (Modern Haiku 40(1), (2009), p. 43), in a playful ASCII-art style reflective of the NFT market. 

(ASCII text generated by patorjk.com.)

QED.
